data.description: Located on the Manzanita-Neahkahnie Mt. townline is where you'll find this amazing beach house property. Capture coastal life in the upscale and friendly Neahkahnie Cove neighborhood while surrounded by wilderness and privacy.  This well appointed home is nestled into a thick virgin forest preserve on a cul-de-sac. No traffic! It's a minute ride to the beach! The location is very close to Manzanita Downtown. Oswald West and the Nehalem Bay State Park are minutes away. The lovely bedroom/studio over the garage is a bonus feature. An optional vacation or long term rental? Don't miss the RV electrical hookup already in place with plenty of parking space. This could be your dream beach home or a very desirable rental investment! Please request a feature sheet for additional information.
